{"tid":1698347,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人以前返學成日聽到「Revision Exercises」呢個term？","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:28:08.000Z","uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"235d8d3c66eb7c7d885aec2c8250194579c35413","tid":1698347,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"我而家諗返上嚟其實呢個term嘅grammar其實啱定唔啱？<br />\n<br />\nRevision係一個noun，係指溫習複習<br />\nExercises係一個noun，係指練習、練習題<br />\n<br />\n咁點解Exercises前面係用noun而唔係adjective嘅？<br />\n<br />\n以前唔覺得有問題，而家突然諗起呢樣嘢就有個咁嘅疑問"},{"pid":"7e631caf6c9f8aab01f3563dd24ab98adccbdc0f","tid":1698347,"uid":182715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12acfb48a866e605f40d23c481b17720096f7758","tid":1698347,"uid":58717,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<br />\nForum Administrator 咪又係兩個noun咁拍埋一齊"},{"pid":"e3f911ab7c388f3fe6e357819f514e01000b8998","tid":1698347,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:12:19.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0e982fcfa419866b30a1b730ddb56a09b2b3b2","tid":1698347,"uid":8550,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"Apple pie<br />\n<br />\nApple= noun<br />\nPie = noun"},{"pid":"bffc5ebdcaecefd199795f72ba51bc1b1ecd528a","tid":1698347,"uid":253035,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"Compound Noun?<br />\n<br />\n利申 : DSE英文2"},{"pid":"115aa270ead83998f778a21d622f7b6a4a4922d0","tid":1698347,"uid":106027,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"compound noun？"},{"pid":"08fdf96a23b5dd152d6b5dd5d1f529e3eb9eae02","tid":1698347,"uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"我搵到答案了<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hopenglish.com/why-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopenglish.com%2Fwhy-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKzQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=303e1173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hopenglish.com/why-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun</a><br />\n【老師救救我】為什麼兩個名詞可以放在一起？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度寫<br />\n「英文中如果把兩個名詞放在一起，可以用前者修飾後者，或是表示後者是屬於前者的某部分」<br />\n「所以不一定只有形容詞可以修飾名詞，名詞也可以用來修飾名詞。有時候如果換成形容詞，意思反而會天差地遠呢！」<br />\n「下次看到兩個名詞放在一起時，莫驚慌莫害怕，就讓我們祝它們百年好合吧～」<br />\n<br />\n原來如此"},{"pid":"4ae7cf4609e6759a682b54fa36b957e20a058031","tid":1698347,"uid":65354,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"08fdf96a23b5dd152d6b5dd5d1f529e3eb9eae02","tid":1698347,"uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"我搵到答案了<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hopenglish.com/why-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopenglish.com%2Fwhy-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKzQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=303e1173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hopenglish.com/why-is-there-a-noun-before-a-noun</a><br />\n【老師救救我】為什麼兩個名詞可以放在一起？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度寫<br />\n「英文中如果把兩個名詞放在一起，可以用前者修飾後者，或是表示後者是屬於前者的某部分」<br />\n「所以不一定只有形容詞可以修飾名詞，名詞也可以用來修飾名詞。有時候如果換成形容詞，意思反而會天差地遠呢！」<br />\n「下次看到兩個名詞放在一起時，莫驚慌莫害怕，就讓我們祝它們百年好合吧～」<br />\n<br />\n原來如此"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"Art Museum"},{"pid":"9f10301149677723c1870b747b760653d3a452b8","tid":1698347,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:25:48.000Z","